OL,3,CClaire Chick's murder triggers 'urgent
OL,4,Cpolice review' into stalking
OL,6,FOn Friday 25 April, Butler was jailed
OL,7,Ffor 26 years and nine months at
OL,8,FPlymouth Crown Court after pleading
OL,9,Fguilty to the murder of his former
OL,10,Fwife, Claire Chick.
OL,12,FCourt hears of months of missed
OL,13,Fopportunities
OL,15,FIn the months leading up to her death
OL,16,FClaire had told police that Butler was
OL,17,Fleaving threatening voice notes, phone
OL,18,Fcalls, e-mails and hanging around
OL,19,Foutside her house.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
