OL,3,CClaire Chick's murder triggers 'urgent
OL,4,Cpolice review' into stalking
OL,6,FThe court also heard that Butler
OL,7,Fplaced a tracking device on Claire's
OL,8,Fcar and told her he knew her exact
OL,9,Fmovements which left her "frightened".
OL,11,FHe was arrested several times by
OL,12,Fpolice and released on bail.
OL,14,FHer final statement, which she signed
OL,15,Fthe day before her death, said: "I
OL,16,Fhonestly feel like Butler will kill me
OL,17,Fif further action is not taken. I am
OL,18,Fconstantly afraid of leaving my house.
OL,19,FI am very fearful of what he has done
OL,20,Fto me and what he will do."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
