OL,6,FButler's sentencing coincides with
OL,7,FNational Stalking Awareness Week,
OL,8,Frunning from 22-25 April.
OL,10,FRecent data from Devon and Cornwall
OL,11,FPolice reveals a concerning 14.4%
OL,12,Fincrease in stalking and harassment
OL,13,Foffences, with 14,457 incidents
OL,14,Frecorded between February 2024-
OL,15,FFebruary 2025.
OL,17,F'We need the behaviour of a lot of men
OL,18,Fto change'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
