OL,6,FAlison Hernandez, Devon and Cornwall
OL,7,FPolice and Crime Commissioner, said:
OL,8,F"When you consider the murder of
OL,9,FClaire Chick, another woman killed at
OL,10,Fthe hands of a man, it represents a
OL,11,Fdeeply-troubling pattern emerging in
OL,12,Fthis region.
OL,14,F"It's particularly distressing because
OL,15,Fany of us could find ourselves in such
OL,16,Fa devastating situation."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
