OL,6,FHernandez highlighted the persistent
OL,7,Fnature of stalking behaviours: "The
OL,8,Freality is perpetrators of stalking
OL,9,Frarely desist, and we know that 98% of
OL,10,Fwomen's murders involve a stalking
OL,11,Felement.
OL,13,F"These individuals represent our most
OL,14,Fdangerous offenders, and we simply
OL,15,Fmust do more to address this. We need
OL,16,Fthe behaviour of a lot of men to
OL,17,Fchange."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
