OL,6,FShe also acknowledged institutional
OL,7,Fresponsibilities: "Many victims
OL,8,Fhesitate to come forward due to fear,
OL,9,Fand often remain with abusive partners
OL,10,Fbecause separation frequently triggers
OL,11,Fescalated violence.
OL,13,F"We must recognise the extraordinarily
OL,14,Fchallenging circumstances many victims
OL,15,Fface, and particularly, we need police
OL,16,Fforces to relentlessly pursue known
OL,17,Frepeat offenders and secure their
OL,18,Fimprisonment. We cannot place the
OL,19,Fentire burden of responsibility on the
OL,20,Fvictims."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
