OL,6,FShe went on to highlight the wider
OL,7,Fissue across not just the region but
OL,8,Fthe whole nation: "The reality is we
OL,9,Fhave got too many men being violent,
OL,10,Fnot just in Devon and Cornwall, but
OL,11,Facross the country and the globe.
OL,13,F"We need some radical solutions to
OL,14,Fdisrupt what's going on in our
OL,15,Fcommunities."
