OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Glen Mayhew
OL,7,Fsaid: "Having met some of Claire's
OL,8,Ffamily following her tragic death, the
OL,9,Fforce has conducted an urgent review
OL,10,Fof all our active stalking
OL,11,Finvestigations.
OL,13,F"This has resulted in immediate
OL,14,Fchanges to our stalking and harassment
OL,15,Fprocedures. New policies have been
OL,16,Fimplemented to ensure we provide
OL,17,Fgreater focus on safeguarding victims,
OL,18,Ftargeting perpetrators at the earliest
OL,19,Fopportunity and encouraging reporting.
