OL,6,FMan Culture, a group in Plymouth,
OL,7,Fworks directly with men and boys
OL,8,Fthrough education, mentorship and
OL,9,Fcommunity engagement to challenge
OL,10,Fharmful stereotypes and encourage
OL,11,Frespect for women.
OL,13,FScott Young, a group member, said:
OL,14,F"Our approach centres on addressing
OL,15,Finappropriate behaviour safely and
OL,16,Fcompassionately. We have a
OL,17,Fresponsibility to call out behaviour."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
