OL,6,FHe said: "Progress is frustratingly
OL,7,Fslow, though inappropriate behaviour
OL,8,Fis being challenged more frequently
OL,9,Fthan in the past.
OL,11,F"When we contextualise these
OL,12,Fbehaviours within a broader culture
OL,13,Fwhere rape and murder represent the
OL,14,Fextreme end of the spectrum.
OL,16,F"Many men dissociate themselves,
OL,17,Fthinking 'I'm not committing rape or
OL,18,Fmurder, therefore I'm not contributing
OL,19,Fto the problem'."
