OL,6,FLyn Gooding, from the charity, said:
OL,7,F"Claire was in fear of her life and
OL,8,Fsadly police didn't intervene soon
OL,9,Fenough in order to protect her, but
OL,10,Fit's really important that other
OL,11,Fpeople who may be experiencing this
OL,12,Ftoday reach out for help and support.
OL,14,F"They've undertaken a review, they,
OL,15,Fyou know, they're committed to giving
OL,16,Fthe right response, and they should be
OL,17,Fheld accountable to it, so make sure
OL,18,Fyou make contact if you are scared
OL,19,Ftoday.
