OL,9,Fthemselves can go to the police and
OL,10,Fmake a Claire's Law request. The
OL,11,Fpolice are then obliged to do an
OL,12,Finvestigation to see if there's
OL,13,Fanything that might highlight a person
OL,14,Fbeing at risk, and then they will make
